{
  "message": "\ud83c\udf31 refactor: replace hardcoded hex colors with design tokens in PodExecTerminal (#3983) (#4000)\n\nExtract the xterm.js terminal theme into a named TERMINAL_THEME constant\n(hex values required by the canvas-based renderer). Replace all 25+\narbitrary Tailwind hex color values in the toolbar, status indicator,\noverlays, and container picker with semantic Tailwind classes (bg-card,\nborder-border, text-muted-foreground, bg-green-700, bg-red-700, etc.).\n\nZero arbitrary hex colors remain in the Tailwind markup; all 20\nremaining hex values live in the TERMINAL_THEME constant where they\nare required by xterm.js.\n\nCloses #3983\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
